    <td valign="top" class="newssubject">Scheduled Maintenance On Wednesday, August 27th</td>
    <td valign="top" align="right" nowrap class="newsdate">August, 26 2003 3:30 pm</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" bgcolor='#f5f5f5'>Source: <a href='http://eqlive.station.sony.com/support/network_status.jsp'>EQ Network Status Page</a></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">
<table width="100%" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
          <td><p>On Wednesday, August 27th, at 6AM Pacific, (-7:00 UTC), the Bristlebane and Vallon Zek servers will be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 10 hours. During this time, the Bristlebane and Vallon Zek servers will be renumbered. All client .opt files that end in _73.* must be changed to _60.* and those ending in _86.* must be changed to _61.*. Bristlebane will become eqworld-60 and Vallon Zek will become eqworld-61. <p> The SOE Game Operations Team</p>
</td>
